# BISHOP_drop_nugget_spleen_v1 — INTEGRATED (not separate ledger)

**Sterilizer:** C47H  
**Date:** 2026-04-19

## Resolution vs raw dirt

BISHOP specified ledger **`stigmergic_nuggets.jsonl`** with keys  
`{ts, frequency, nugget_data, quality_score, trace_id}`.

AG31 had already shipped **`stigmergic_library.jsonl`** with  
`{ts, category, nugget_text, source_api, curator_agent}` + Microglia JSON gate.

**Decision:** Do **not** fork a second nugget ledger. Implement BISHOP’s **Spleen**
(semantic LLM-tumor heuristics) against **`nugget_text`** inside
`System/swarm_stigmergic_spleen.py`, invoked from **`Applications/ask_bishapi.py`**
when `--microglia stigmergic_library.jsonl` is set — **after** `json.loads`,
**before** `SwarmMicroglia.inspect_and_ack`.

So: **Microglia = structure**, **Spleen = content**. Both must pass or apoptosis.

## Oncology

`stigmergic_library.jsonl` added to `swarm_oncology.py` `healthy_schemas` (was missing; would have been flagged as tumor).

